y improve the proposal based on new insights and data.\n\nBy following these steps, the research proposal will be well-rounded and address all necessary aspects of the problem, ensuring a comprehensive and clear presentation of the research plan.", role='assistant', tool_calls=None, function_call=None, provider_specific_fields=None)'.
