tematic literature reviews, which help bridge the gap between research and practical applications.\n\nI am particularly passionate about leveraging digital twins as "digital playgrounds" to navigate the complexities of modern manufacturing. By employing intelligent digital models, I aim to enhance the reconfiguration of brownfield systems and improve the overall lifecycle management of industrial assets. My goal is to create robust, adaptable systems that can respond to the ever-evolving demands of the industrial landscape, ultimately driving efficiency and innovation in automation.)']But you do not have to communcate with other agents.
